%section.conteinar
  .header
    .header__logo
      = image_tag "/logo.png", alt: "Rails icon", class: "image", width: "185px", height: "49px"
  %h2.registration  会員情報入力
  .contents
    = form_for(@user, url: member_signup_index_path, method: :get, html: {class: "address-form", id: "signup-form"}) do |f|
      .address__main
        = f.label :name, "ニックネーム", class: "address__main__label" 
        %span.address__main__require 必須
        = f.text_field :name, class: "address__main__input", placeholder:"例）メルカリ太郎"
      
      .address__main.form
        = f.label :name, "メールアドレス", class: "address__main__label" 
        %span.address__main__require 必須
        = f.text_field :name, class: "address__main__input", placeholder:"PC・携帯どちらでも可"

      .address__main.form
        = f.label :name, "パスワード", class: "address__main__label" 
        %span.address__main__require 必須
        = f.text_field :name, class: "address__main__input", placeholder:"7文字以上の半角英数字"
        %p.address__main__text※ 英字と数字の両方を含めて設定してください
        %input.icon-check{ type: 'checkbox' }
        = f.label :name, "パスワードを表示する", class: "address__main__label"

      .address__main.group
        %h3.chapter 本人確認用
        %p.single-text
          安心・安全にご利用いただくために、お客さまの本人情報の登録にご協力ください。他のお客さまに公開されることはありません。

      .address__main.form
        = f.label :name, "お名前（全角）", class: "address__main__label" 
        %span.address__main__require 必須
        .address__sub
          = f.text_field :name, class: "address__main__input--hurf", placeholder:"例）山田"
          = f.text_field :name, class: "address__main__input--hurf", placeholder:"例）彩"


      .address__main.form
        = f.label :name, "お名前カナ（全角）", class: "address__main__label" 
        %span.address__main__require 必須
        .address__sub
          = f.text_field :name, class: "address__main__input--hurf", placeholder:"例）ヤマダ"
          = f.text_field :name, class: "address__main__input--hurf", placeholder:"例）アヤ"

      .address__main.form
        = f.label :name, "生年月日", class: "address__main__label" 
        %span.address__main__require 必須
        .address__sub
          = f.text_field :name, class: "address__main__input--shurf", placeholder:"--"
          %span.birthday 年
          = f.text_field :name, class: "address__main__input--shurf", placeholder:"--"
          %span.birthday 月
          = f.text_field :name, class: "address__main__input--shurf", placeholder:"--"
          %span.birthday 日
      %p.form__info
        ※ 本人情報は正しく入力してください。会員登録後、修正するにはお時間を頂く場合があります。
      
      .contents__sub
        .contents__sub__text
          %p
            「次へ進む」のボタンを押すことにより、
            = link_to "利用規約", "", class: "contents__sub__text__2" 
            に
            %br
            同意したものとみなします
            = f.submit "次へ進む", class: "contents__sub__btn"

          .contents__sub__right
            %p
              = link_to "本人情報の登録について＞", "", class: "contents__sub__right__link "
          .contents__sub__footer
            %p 
              This site is protected by reCAPTCHA and the Google
              = link_to "Privacy Policy", "", class: "contents__sub__footer__bottom"
              and
              = link_to "Terms of Service", "", class: "contents__sub__footer__bottom"
              apply.




  = render 'layouts/second_footer'

